    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09040"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1787-12-27">1787  г. 27 декабря.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>№ 80. Симбирскаго и <placeName ref="places.xml#ufa01">Уфимскаго</placeName>—об отдаче Меленских казенных винокуренных заводов
                <note type="editorial">
                    Catherine most likely writes about distilleries in <placeName ref="places.xml#dim01">Melekess</placeName> (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#brokef01">Entsiklopedicheskii slovar' Brokgauza i Efrona</title>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>
                на аренду купцу <persName ref="people.xml#ust01">Устинову</persName>
                <note type="editorial">
                    A.V. Khrapovitskii's under <date when-custom="1788-01-30">January 30 1788</date> notes that <rs ref="people.xml#vya01">General Procurator</rs> and <persName ref="people.xml#suk01">Ober Procurator Sukharev</persName> were scolded by Catherine for selling the distilleries (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#dnevni02">Dnevnik A.V. Khrapovitskago s 18 ianvaria 1782 po 17 sentiabria 1793 goda</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 37.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>.</p>
        </body>
